'''PHP许可证'''（PHP License）是指在[[PHP|PHP]]语言发布时所使用的[[软件许可证|软件许可证]]。根据[[自由软件基金会|自由软件基金会]]的分类，PHP许可证属于[[许可证兼容性|与GPL不兼容]]的自由软件许可证，因为许可证限制了对“PHP”一词的使用<ref name="gpl-incompat">{{cite web | title = GPL-Incompatible, Free Software Licenses | url = http://www.gnu.org/licenses/license-list.html#GPLIncompatibleLicenses | work = Various Licenses and Comments about Them | publisher = Free Software Foundation | accessdate = 2011-10-23 | archive-date = 2009-07-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090716201618/http://www.gnu.org/licenses/license-list.html#GPLIncompatibleLicenses | dead-url = no }}</ref>；另外，PHP许可证也被[[开放源代码促进会|开放源代码促进会]]认可为一种开源许可证<ref name="osi">{{cite web | title = OSI-approved licenses by name | url = http://www.opensource.org/licenses/alphabetical | work = Alphabetized list of open source licenses approved by the Open Source Initiative (OSI) | accessdate = 2011-10-23 | archive-date = 2011-04-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110428141712/http://opensource.org/licenses/alphabetical | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

